Synopsis:
Daniel a young boy has gone through life unnoticed for as long as he could remember. This causes him no small amount of pain, but he still remains strong because he has a goal. Watch as his goal becomes more a struggle of life and death as he learns just how dangerous the world is. But Daniel isn’t one to shy away from hard work and he will continue forward. He will not stop. He will win.
